' Methodology Diagram 03 — Scientific-method loop (activity).
'
' Shows the falsificationist hypothesis-experiment-refute cycle the
' methodology runs continuously. Each iteration either expands the
' traceability ledger, expands the mechanized arm, or expands the
' persistent corpus. The loop never deletes evidence; it only re-classifies.
'
' Render:
'   plantuml -tsvg docs/theory/slashing/methodology/diagrams/03-scientific-method-loop.puml

@startuml 03-scientific-method-loop
!theme plain

skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor       #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityBorderColor           #333333
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF7EE
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor    #E65100
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor           #FFE0B2
skinparam NoteBorderColor               #E65100
skinparam defaultFontName "sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

title Scientific-method loop — hypothesize → search → falsify → record

start

:Derive candidate property φ from\nmodels / spec / threat model;
note right
  Candidate sources:
  • Rocq module under development
  • TLA⁺ spec invariant
  • Bug-fix manifest entry
  • STRIDE / attack-tree leaf
  • Open Sage finding
end note

:Choose tool by shape × domain × budget;
note right
  Decision tree:
  • unbounded semantic → Rocq
  • finite bounded → TLA⁺ + TLC
  • per-function Rust → Kani
  • byte-level / structure → libFuzzer
  • multi-step lifecycle → Hypothesis
  • single-step property → proptest
  • concurrency interleaving → Loom
  • combinatorial witness → Sage
end note

:Tool.search(φ);

if (Refuted (witness w)) then (yes)
  :Classify w under threat-model vocabulary;
  if (Class = unexpected?) then (yes)
    #FFEBEE:Halt — escalate audit;
    stop
  else (no)
  endif

  :Attempt reproduction on Rust\nproduction path;

  switch (Assign traceability status)
    case (confirmed_current_bug)
      #FFEBEE:Fix Rust source +\nadd pre_fix_bug_N.rs +\nupdate Rocq/TLA⁺/threat docs;
    case (confirmed_fixed_bug)
      :Keep pre_fix_bug_N.rs;
    case (projection_risk_guarded)
      :Keep guard test + spec text;
    case (assumption_counterexample)
      :Strengthen theorem precondition;
    case (proof_or_model_strengthening)
      #EEF2FF:Promote to Rocq theorem\nand/or TLA⁺ invariant;
    case (not_reproduced_in_rust)
      :Record only;
    case (model_boundary)
      :Document boundary;
    case (needs_source_audit)
      #FFE0B2:Escalate audit;
  endswitch

  :Append ledger entry +\npersist fixture to corpus;
  :Re-run tool;\nverify w no longer surfaces\n(or surfaces with expected\npost-fix status);

else (no — bounded search exhausted)
  if (Cost budget exhausted?) then (yes)
    :Record "no counterexample under bounds B";
    :Strengthen hypothesis OR\nincrease budget OR\nretire search;
  else (no)
    :Continue exhaustion;
  endif
endif

:Update spec / verification doc\nif φ changed status;

if (More candidate properties?) then (yes)
  :Loop back to next iteration;
  stop
else (no)
  stop
endif

@enduml
